        <Parent_String>poetry and poems [300417751], genres for literature [300200882], genres in literature and performing arts [300055907], concepts in the arts and humanities [300056107], Associated Concepts (hierarchy name) [300055126], Associated Concepts Facet [300264086]</Parent_String>
